## 4. VCN-LUPINE Compression Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Input["Input: Raw Braid Data"]
        A["1 MB per strand\nUncompressed"]
    end
    
    subgraph Compression["Compression Stages"]
        B["Stage 1: Delta Encoding\nTemporal difference\n~2x reduction"]
        C["Stage 2: RLE Compression\nRun-length encoding\n~2.5x additional"]
        D["Total after Delta+RLE: ~5x reduction\n~200 KB"]
        E["Stage 3: Reed-Solomon ECC\nAdd parity data\n~1.2x overhead\n~240 KB"]
        F["Stage 4: ChaCha20 Encryption\n256-bit key\n~240 KB (minimal overhead)"]
        G["Stage 5: H.264 Hardware Encode\nNVENC/VAAPI\n50x reduction\n~4.8 KB"]
        H["Stage 6: MKV Containerization\nAdd metadata\n~5 KB final"]
    end
    
    subgraph Output["Output"]
        I["22 KB per strand\n45x total compression"]
    end
    
    subgraph Hardware["Hardware Acceleration"]
        J["NVENC\nNVIDIA RTX 4090\nqfox-1"]
        K["VAAPI\nAMD iGPU\nsteamdeck"]
    end
    
    %% Flow
    A --> B
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D --> E
    E --> F
    F --> G
    G --> H
    H --> I
    
    G --> |"Uses"| J
    G --> |"Uses"| K
```

