## 7. Hermes Request Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant LoadBalancer
    participant HermesAPI
    participant FrameDispatcher
    participant RayCluster
    participant ModelActor
    participant VCNPipeline
    
    User->>LoadBalancer: HTTPS POST /generate
    LoadBalancer->>HermesAPI: Forward request
    HermesAPI->>HermesAPI: Validate request
    HermesAPI->>HermesAPI: Check rate limit
    HermesAPI->>FrameDispatcher: Select model
    FrameDispatcher->>FrameDispatcher: Lookup MODEL_REGISTRY
    FrameDispatcher->>RayCluster: Get or create actor
    RayCluster->>ModelActor: Schedule task
    ModelActor->>VCNPipeline: Process frames (if video)
    VCNPipeline->>VCNPipeline: Delta+RLE->RS->ChaCha20->H.264
    VCNPipeline-->>ModelActor: Compressed ObjectRef
    ModelActor->>ModelActor: Load model (lazy)
    ModelActor->>ModelActor: Generate tokens
    ModelActor-->>RayCluster: Return ObjectRef
    RayCluster-->>FrameDispatcher: Stream tokens
    FrameDispatcher-->>HermesAPI: Aggregate results
    HermesAPI-->>User: SSE Stream / JSON Response
```

